---
name: Bug Report
description: Create a report for a bug encountered in the Service Router Operator.
title: "[BUG] - [Brief description of the bug]"
labels: bug
assignees: ''

body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        ## Bug Description
        Please provide a clear and concise description of the bug.

  - type: input
    id: reproduction-steps
    attributes:
      label: "Reproduction Steps"
      placeholder: "List the steps to reproduce the bug..."

  - type: input
    id: expected-behaviour
    attributes:
      label: "Expected Behaviour"
      placeholder: "What did you expect to happen?"

  - type: input
    id: actual-behaviour
    attributes:
      label: "Actual Behaviour"
      placeholder: "What actually happened?"

  - type: input
    id: environment
    attributes:
      label: "Environment"
      placeholder: "Please specify the environment (e.g., Kubernetes version, OS, etc.)"

  - type: input
    id: additional-info
    attributes:
      label: "Additional Information"
      placeholder: "Any other information that might be helpful (logs, screenshots, etc.)"

---

name: Feature Request
description: Create a request for a new feature in the Service Router Operator.
title: "[FEATURE] - [Brief description of the feature]"
labels: enhancement
assignees: ''

body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        ## Feature Description
        Please provide a clear and concise description of the feature you would like to request.

  - type: input
    id: use-case
    attributes:
      label: "Use Case"
      placeholder: "Describe the use case for this feature..."

  - type: input
    id: benefits
    attributes:
      label: "Benefits"
      placeholder: "What benefits will this feature provide?"

  - type: input
    id: additional-info
    attributes:
      label: "Additional Information"
      placeholder: "Any other information that might be helpful (mockups, links, etc.)"